Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0010,,我拿到解毒劑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才讓爸爸喝下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 我的心情很沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在竟然要將形同兄弟的你扭送警局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 你大概接受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這確實是我的真實想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份心意 確實是你善良的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 我有個請求 雖然這很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能給我點時間 讓我去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才還在防備著他 以為他會像走投無路的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時準備反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然平安從那貧民窟回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能實施那計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓他放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看準機會一口氣用小刀幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很後悔 對以前走過的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為生在一個貧窮的環境裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中就懷著無意義的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會做出這樣的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然想毒害養育自己的恩人 搶奪他的財產
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了表示我的悔意 我回來自首了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我要逃亡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外國也好別的地方也好 都沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確…確實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想贖罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生 小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要相信這傢伙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你一臉「你誰啊」的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先來自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛管閒事的史比特瓦根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為擔心喬斯達先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從倫敦貧民窟一直跟到這裏來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生 我喜歡你的天真 所以給你個忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生在黑暗街 長在黑暗街
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見過無數的惡黨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以憑味道就能分辨壞人和好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙很臭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比嘔吐物還難聞的味道撲鼻而來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:04:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還從沒見過這樣的邪惡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環境所逼才當壞人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了！這人是天生的邪惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得這個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從這個東洋人口中得到賣給你毒藥的證言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你傾注了不下於親兒子的愛情和期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你還要靜養的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回寢室休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到自己的兒子被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 接下來的事就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人不會被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵上的三顆痣 以及他的臉相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是天生的強運者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 至少希望你能親手給我扣上手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在我們七年交情的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生 小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的能力真是有極限的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我短暫的人生裏學到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人越是玩弄陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就越會在預料之外的事態失足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為超越人類的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不當人類了！JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超越人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石面具！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在你那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射殺他！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 用你的鮮血啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一把小刀 一般情況是能避開的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻被石面具吸引了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而您就替我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…去世的媽媽的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一刀刺中要害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我來了還發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達卿 我早就跟他說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如當時我將迪奧·布朗度的父親放流荒島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧·布朗度的父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當上警察沒多久的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮住了一個想拿那顆戒指去抵押的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是迪奧的父親 達利奧·布朗度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是我的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是跟妻子一對的結婚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就被那個叫布朗度小偷抵押了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗度？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗度是喬斯達卿的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個對馬車事故幸災樂禍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁機打劫財物的狡猾的惡人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有沒有跟你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個戒指是我送給他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 當然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是彌天大謊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個戒指是我送給他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是無辜的 請釋放了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？為什麼替他圓謊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我也出身貧困 也許會做出跟他一樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拿去賣掉 為家人買點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再當壞人 要當個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達卿是在知道一切內情的情況下收養迪奧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生來了就會得救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 不要恨迪奧 是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的親生兒子 所以對你格外的嚴厲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迪奧看來 也許這反而是一種歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會做出這樣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將迪奧安葬在布朗度先生的墓旁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有遺憾了 能死在兒子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…懷抱裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達卿！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的善良卻帶來如此的不幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收養迪奧是做錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣死了就毫無意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位父親的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他的兒子喬納森·喬斯達全部繼承下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會成為他的強大意志 自豪和未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說 我最討厭那種一遇到挫折就痛哭的少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這對父子不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不為自己所做的事情後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是最可愛最天真的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍…屍體…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧·布朗度的屍體不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生 快躲離窗戶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官的頭被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這傢伙復活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 中了那麼多槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 他肯定拿著什麼武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 快開槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪…迪奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊 JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開槍！開槍啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明打中了頭部的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:12:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 我完全不知道發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到如此強大的力量了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是石面具賜予的！是你父親的血賜予的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UUUURRRRYYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吸取人類的精氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧究竟成為了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大腦中異常的混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀刺…父親的死…血…迪奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石面具…研究記錄…大腦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的能力…未知的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧已經不是人類了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UURRYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打不過他的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過那樣的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒見過能超越那股力量的魔物！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 實話說我也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 迪奧 不能讓你留在這個世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的責任 我要收拾你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只會送命的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦！肯定是石面具的骨針
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從大腦激發了人類的潛藏能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 打倒迪奧的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍…屍體…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血…我要喝血！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸到血就行了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對手是怪物 但還是很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 請給予我更強大的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要更強大的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧已經不是人類 是魔物了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓迪奧繼續增加殺戮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋…擋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中將他刺穿擋住了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 他頭部的傷口癒合了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死身！完全的不死身！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧弱啊 貧弱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jo——Jo！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再玩一會 再讓我用這股美妙的力量玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也還不知道能有多強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是玩弄計謀就越會失足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是有極限的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做無謂掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別光躲在窗簾後面打顫 出來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是計謀 是勇氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織在被燒焦的同時再生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這個才是不死之身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點火不能打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 史比特瓦根！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本來是無關的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能往上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火勢會往整座宅邸蔓延的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生 你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來啊 迪奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧！不能讓你和你的力量放進人世！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我的注意力從同伴身上引開？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成全你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的燒傷 就吸取你的血來治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用 沒用 沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點高度 我跳下去也毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反 被火勢和高度逼得無路可走的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 您安息吧 請在這場大火中前往天堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請將力量賦予火焰 助我成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生 你究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…難道你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能那樣做！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,URRRRRRY！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧弱啊 貧弱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間 JoJo的大腦裏閃過自己的一幕幕青春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的青春 是跟迪奧一起度過的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 就來為我的青春做個了結！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達先生在想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓火勢來得更猛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要火勢大到超越那魔物的回復力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能打倒迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此他爬到屋頂等待火勢燒遍整座宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢打這樣的主意！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的祖先代代生活的喬斯達邸正在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親死了 我一無所有 失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這條命！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條性命也一併燃燒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為代價 迪奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要封印你的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Bye JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有一瞬間 我實在為你的覺悟震驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父親的屍體旁 流著高興的淚水死去吧 蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超越人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死身 不老不死 我能支配這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 這是你給我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧！我回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我不會鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧 你的命數盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把刀…這把刀是你刺死爸爸的刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,URYYY！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙臂的骨頭都碎了 身上都著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是力量沒有減小絲毫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 很好 我們一起投入烈火中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 死的只會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論火勢有多大 還是應該有能逃出去的能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！給予我最後的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼叫 忘情的吼叫！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼叫的聲音傳達給父親的靈魂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是無意中利用了從小長大的府邸的構造嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹬牆了！蹬過去的方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬斯達家的守護神 慈愛的女神像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…你這混蛋竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了…
